STATE

TENCH 2016-0899 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 31, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On appellant's amended motion for appointment of counsel. Motion granted. Kimberly S. Rigby appointed to represent appellant for the purpose of filing an application for reopening pursuant to S.Ct. Prac.R. 11.06.
